Package lu.softec.maven.mavenizer.analyzer.mavenasm

Interface Summary
FileAwareClassVisitor Interface extending ClassVisitor to be able to supply to the visitor, the file containing the currently visited class and the ordinal position of the class in that file.
MavenDependencyWalker This interface is similar to the ClassWalker interface, but on a list of maven dependencies.
 

Class Summary
AbstractClassWalkVisitorListener Abstract class extending AbstractClassWalkListener and providing basic functionalities to parse classes using a ClassReader and a FileAwareClassVisitor.
ClassDependencyVisitor Implements a FileAwareClassVisitor that agregate dependencies in a ClassAnalyser
ClassInventoryVisitor Implements a FileAwareClassVisitor that agregate visited class name in a ClassAnalyser
ClassWalkDependencyVisitorListener Specialized AbstractClassWalkVisitorListener using a ClassDependencyVisitor to visit classes and logging informational and error messages into a Log.
ClassWalkInventoryVisitorListener Specialized AbstractClassWalkVisitorListener using a ClassInventoryVisitor to visit classes and logging informational and error messages into a Log.
DefaultMavenDependencyWalker Default implementation of MavenDependencyWalker Dependencies are resolved as needed.
